/***** Global Balloon Design -- START *****/
/* Title text */

	border-bottom: 1px solid #DBDBDB !important;
}

	font-family: "Cambria","Georgia",serif !important;
	color: #000 !important;
	font-size: 15px !important;

.walkme-custom-no-buttons .walkme-custom-balloon-title{

}

	height: auto !important;
}

.walkme-custom-side-border,
.walkme-custom-balloon-separator{
	display: none !important;
}

.walkme-custom-balloon-buttons-wrapper{
	text-align: center !important;
	height: 43px !important;
}

.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-weak-button.walkme-custom-balloon-back-button.walkme-action-back{
	display: none !important;
}

.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-normal-button.walkme-custom-balloon-next-button.walkme-action-next,
.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-normal-button.walkme-custom-balloon-done-button.walkme-action-done{	
	height: 25px !important;

	margin-top: 0px !important;
	background: -moz-linear-gradient(#FFF, #E5E5E5) !important;

	font-family: "Helvetica Neue","Arial","Helvetica","Verdana",sans-serif !important;

	color: #000 !important;

	background: -o-linear-gradient(#FFF, #F2F2F2) !important;
	background: linear-gradient(#FFF, #F2F2F2) !important;
	background-color: #F2F2F2 !important;

}
